data.description: Country living at its best with over four acres! It's in the Model School District! Check out this super nice three bedroom / two bath home! The two bathrooms have recently been renovated! The home is only eight years old and is on a permanent foundation & is total electric. It has a nice size front yard! There use to be another mobile home on the property, so it has another septic tank, public water, & electricity hook-ups. There is also a well on the property, it does not have a pump. It has a huge back yard with so many options. You can sit on your back deck and have a peaceful evening, while you enjoy watching the deer and other wildlife. It's only about 5 to 7 minutes from the down town area. There are a couple of buildings in the back for extra storage. The gray building will not remain with property. The seller will need two weeks after the closing to get moved out.
